Question:

A Department has Employees. If department is closed, employees still exist. What relationship?

Answer:

ğŸ‘‰ Aggregation

Code:
class Employee {
    String name;
}

class Department {
    List<Employee> employees;

    Department(List<Employee> employees) {
        this.employees = employees;
    }
}


ğŸ‘‰ Interview line:

â€œThis is aggregation because employees have independent lifecycle.â€